<b>Collider.JAM</b> is a JavaScript game framework
that tries to keep the fun of game jamming and prototyping.

It is a fun way to prototype and create games.

Also it conceals some rough JavaScript edges,
making it a good candidate for language introduction.

To start, check out <a href="#.getting-started">Getting Started</a>.


